OL,3,CSwinney admits he cannot guarantee
OL,4,Cchild poverty will continue to reduce
OL,6,FFirst Minister John Swinney has said
OL,7,Fhe cannot guarantee child poverty will
OL,8,Fcontinue to reduce, blaming the impact
OL,9,Fof Westminster policies.
OL,11,FMr Swinney has pinpointed the
OL,12,Feradication of child poverty as his
OL,13,Fguiding principle since taking office
OL,14,Flast year, and he has repeatedly
OL,15,Ftouted Scotland's falling rate in
OL,16,Frecent figures as being unique in the
OL,17,FUK.
