OL,3,CSwinney admits he cannot guarantee
OL,4,Cchild poverty will continue to reduce
OL,6,FHowever, the figures released earlier
OL,7,Fthis year do not cover the period of
OL,8,FMr Swinney's premiership, which began
OL,9,Fin May after the downfall of Humza
OL,10,FYousaf.
OL,12,FThe statistics showed relative child
OL,13,Fpoverty fell to 23% in March of last
OL,14,Fyear, but that was well above the
OL,15,FScottish Government's interim target
OL,16,Fof 18% by 2023-24.
