OL,3,CSwinney admits he cannot guarantee
OL,4,Cchild poverty will continue to reduce
OL,6,FSpeaking to the PA news agency ahead
OL,7,Fof the SNP's annual conference, the
OL,8,FFirst Minister said he hopes child
OL,9,Fpoverty will continue to reduce in
OL,10,FScotland.
OL,12,FBut he added: "I have to be candid
OL,13,Fthat there are pressures that are
OL,14,Fdrawing it in the opposite direction,
OL,15,Fnot least of which is the actions of
OL,16,Fthe UK Government ` and that's one of
OL,17,Fthe strongest arguments for
OL,18,Findependence.
