OL,6,F"We'll give it our all, but I have to
OL,7,Ftake account of the fact that there
OL,8,Fmight well be a prevailing direction
OL,9,Fthat can be a real challenge as a
OL,10,Fconsequence."
OL,12,FThe First Minister and others in the
OL,13,FScottish Government have consistently
OL,14,Ftaken aim at the UK Government over
OL,15,Fchild poverty, particularly around
OL,16,Ftheir refusal to abolish the two-child
OL,17,Fbenefit cap.
