OL,3,CSwinney admits he cannot guarantee
OL,4,Cchild poverty will continue to reduce
OL,6,FWhile recent reports suggest the UK
OL,7,FGovernment is considering replacing
OL,8,Fthe cap with a new tapered system when
OL,9,FChancellor Rachel Reeves unveils her
OL,10,FBudget in November, the Scottish
OL,11,FGovernment has committed to mitigating
OL,12,Fthe effects of the policy north of the
OL,13,Fborder from early next year, likely by
OL,14,Fintroducing a new benefit.
OL,16,FThe First Minister also committed to
OL,17,Fpublishing a child poverty plan before
OL,18,Fthe next election.
