OL,6,FA spokesman for the UK Government
OL,7,Fsaid: "We are working closely with and
OL,8,Fsupporting the Scottish Government
OL,9,Fthrough the largest real-terms
OL,10,Fsettlement in the history of
OL,11,Fdevolution.
OL,13,F"The UK government is determined to
OL,14,Fbring down child poverty.
OL,16,F"We've already uprated benefits,
OL,17,Fincreased the national minimum wage
OL,18,Fand are supporting 700,000 of the
OL,19,Fpoorest families by introducing a Fair
OL,20,FRepayment Rate on universal credit
OL,21,Fdeductions.
